Red Team â€“ Offensive security professionals who simulate real-world attacks.

Blue Team â€“ Defensive security experts who protect systems from attacks.

Purple Team â€“ A collaboration between Red and Blue teams to improve security.

Security Operations Center (SOC) â€“ Monitors and responds to security incidents.

